{"tid":275810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法援署拒郭卓堅未來三年法援申請","createTime":"2017-06-08T10:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T13:08:07.000Z","uid":59648,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"201a51246c588279f02c630d9d9ed70383688b29","tid":275810,"uid":59648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:21:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】法援署拒絕長洲居民郭卓堅未來三年所有關於司法覆核的法援申請。<br />\n<br />\n法援署去信郭卓堅，指他過去三年提出超過20宗法援申請，濫用《法律援助條例》所提供的服務，未來三年將不會接受他所有關於司法覆核的法援申請。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅認為法援署的決定不公平，會去信提出上訴，如不獲受理，將提出司法覆核，強調不會因為沒有法援就放棄司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=224079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D224079&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjnchv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=18370815\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D224079&h=865626c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=224079</a>"},{"pid":"6abdda8d1dba5b08527bfc62a0efb9c1c673144d","tid":275810,"uid":53374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【Now新聞台】法援署拒絕長洲居民郭卓堅未來三年所有關於司法覆核的法援申請。<br />\n<br />\n法援署去信郭卓堅，指他過去三年提出超過20宗法援申請，濫用《法律援助條例》所提供的服務，未來三年將不會接受他所有關於司法覆核的法援申請。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅認為法援署的決定不公平，會去信提出上訴，如不獲受理，將提出司法覆核，強調不會因為沒有法援就放棄司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=224079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D224079&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjnchv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=18370815\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D224079&h=865626c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=224079</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c144c3d19d9cce4484855012373ad3db1678f1c","tid":275810,"uid":73092,"like":0,"di